Adequately plan and thoroughly study the feasibility of each project before proposing it to be included as one of the projects to be funded by the 20% LGDF;

Ensure proper coordination among concerned offices;

Ensure immediate action and exert additional effort for the timely implement-tation of the projects; and

Ensure the full utilization of the appropriated amounts for the benefit of the constituents in terms of PPAs to be implemented under 20% LGDF.

